trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for all toolbox items associated with an activity in a workflow designer.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en basisklasse for alle verktøykassen elementer som er knyttet til en aktivitet i en arbeidsflyt designer.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] All toolbox items associated with an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class are derived from ActivityToolboxItem.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Alle verktøykassen elementer som er tilknyttet en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>klassen som er avledet fra ActivityToolboxItem.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: This class displays a graphical representation of an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class in the toolbox of a design-time environment and creates an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> class it is associated with when a user drags it onto the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen viser en grafisk fremstilling av en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>klasse i verktøykassen i et miljø med utformingen og oppretter en forekomst av den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>klassen den er knyttet når en bruker drar til utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>

trans-unit.source: The activity toolbox item typically represents an activity to create when invoked on a design-mode document.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet verktøykasseelementet representerer vanligvis en aktivitet for å opprette når den startes på et utformingsmodus-dokument.

trans-unit.source: This class inherits directly from the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen arver direkte fra <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>klasse.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor for the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem> class.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktør for <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem>klassen.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"></xref> class that creates the specified type of <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> component.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"> </xref> klassen som oppretter den angitte typen av <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> komponent.

trans-unit.source: The type of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that the toolbox item will create.
trans-unit.target: Typen for den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> som oppretter verktøykasseelementet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"></xref> class by using the specified <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> and <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av den angitte <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> og <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: When ActivityToolboxItem is called, it deserializes the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Når ActivityToolboxItem kalles, deserializes verktøykasseelementet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"></xref> that holds information to deserialize the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Runtime.Serialization.SerializationInfo"> </xref> som inneholder informasjon deserialisering verktøykasseelementet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext> that provides the deserialization context for the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>som gir deserialisering kontekst verktøykassen-element.</xref:System.Runtime.Serialization.StreamingContext>

trans-unit.source: Creates an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> component or an array of <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> components when the toolbox item is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> -komponent eller en matrise av <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> komponenter når verktøykasseelementet startes.

trans-unit.source: The CreateComponentsCore method returns the component or components that the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem> creates.
trans-unit.target: Metoden CreateComponentsCore returnerer komponenten eller komponenter som den <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem>oppretter.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"></xref> to host the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"> </xref> som vert for verktøykasseelementet.

trans-unit.source: An array of created <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Opprette en matrise av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Creates an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> component or an array of <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> components that generate a dialog box on the design surface when the toolbox item is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> -komponent eller en matrise av <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> komponenter som genererer en dialogboks på utformingen surface når verktøykasseelementet startes.

trans-unit.source: Activity designer developers can override this method to display a dialog box when the toolbox item is dragged onto the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Aktivitet designer utviklere kan overstyre denne metoden for å vise en dialogboks når verktøykasseelementet slippes på utformingsoverflaten.

trans-unit.source: Unless overridden, this method has the same behavior as <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Med mindre overstyres, er denne metoden på samme måte som <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityToolboxItem.CreateComponentsCore%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"></xref> to host the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"> </xref> som vert for verktøykasseelementet.

trans-unit.source: An array of created <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Opprette en matrise av <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets the associated display name for the Toolbox item in the Toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Henter det tilknyttede visningsnavnet for verktøykasseelementet i verktøykassen.

trans-unit.source: The type of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> to retrieve the display name for.
trans-unit.target: Typen for den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> til å hente visningsnavnet for.

trans-unit.source: String representing the display name for the Toolbox item
trans-unit.target: Streng som representerer visningsnavnet for verktøykassen-elementet

trans-unit.source: Gets the associated Image that is used to represent the Toolbox item in the Toolbox.
trans-unit.target: Henter tilknyttede bildet som brukes til å representere verktøykasseelementet i verktøykassen.

trans-unit.source: The type of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> to retrieve the Toolbox image for.
trans-unit.target: Typen for den <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> til å hente verktøykassen bildet for.

trans-unit.source: Image object displayed in the Toolbox for a Toolbox item
trans-unit.target: Bildeobjekt som vises i verktøykassen for et verktøykassen-element
